              "a7eb25a2b1472bcd917e359463ed33b3e2393bdf",
              "d81834cdcc4667bd4b48a5a93b9fab280313e1a4"
            ],
            "confidence": "high"
          },
          {
            "text": "Prune now shrugs off assets that 404 mid-delete instead of failing the release, keeping nightly publishes green when GitHub garbage-collects assets out from under us.",
            "commit_shas": [
              "ac61ac34f8980288b3c0de16c352756ddedd6e04"
            ],
            "confidence": "high"
          },
          {
            "text": "Added a manual Republish GitHub Pages workflow backed by an allow-empty commit path in the gh-pages retry script, giving operators a one-click recovery when Pages gets into a bad state.",
